# TRN menu search (>5 items)

When adding or editing a **dropdown, overflow, or glass menu** under **`extension/src/webview/`**:

## Threshold

- Show a search field when the menu has **more than 5 items** (6+).
- Canonical constant: **`TRN_MENU_SEARCH_MIN_ITEMS`** and **`shouldShowTrnMenuSearch(itemCount)`** in **`ui/TRN/TRNMenuSearch.tsx`**.

## Use shared primitives

| Pattern | Component |
|---------|-----------|
| Sectioned toolbar / shell menus | **`TRNSearchableMenuShell`** + **`TRNMenuFilterableSection`** + **`TRNMenuSearchableRow`** |
| Simple option lists (`TRNSelect`, listbox) | **`shouldShowTrnMenuSearch`**, **`TRNMenuSearchField`**, **`matchesTrnMenuSearch`**, **`TRNMenuScrollRegion`** (see **`GlassDropdown`**) |
| Filter hook per row | **`useTRNMenuItemMatches(label, keywords?)`** |

Pass accurate **`itemCount`** to **`TRNSearchableMenuShell`** (include sections, presets, and dynamic rows). When search is shown, scroll the **body** via **`TRNMenuScrollRegion`** with **`edgeAutoScroll`** — not the sticky search header.

## Menus that already follow this

Shell hamburger, **`TRNSelect`**, **`GlassDropdown`**, **`DropdownList`**, **`IconMenu`**, Studio/Telemetry overflow, **`WorkbenchLayoutMenu`**, assistant tools, rotation preview / Animation Lab model and environment pickers.

## Small menus (≤5 items)

Do **not** add search (e.g. five-option tag filter, two-item Serial Port Manager menu).

## Communication

**Always DO NOT respond in Chinese.** Use **English** and/or **Thai** only — **`communication-language.mdc`**.

Keep **`.cursor/rules/trn-menu-search.mdc`** in sync when editing this file.
